Data notes (not part of the software license):
- StatsBomb open data used in the examples is subject to StatsBomb's open-data
  user agreement (https://github.com/statsbomb/open-data). This repository does
  not redistribute StatsBomb event data.
- Elo ratings referenced in the examples are from eloratings.net.
- The default 0-10 display-scale anchor values were calibrated against aggregate
  crowd-rating quantiles from seriesgraph.com.
